name: Mimz Toolbox
short_description:
The project was made in the end of 2011 and was continued to be developed in 2012. However, I restored my computer which caused me to lose everything including the source code. This isn't developed any longer and is still in the BETA stages.
The music is easily customized and a new user was added to the SQL database online.
Now anyone can long in as a regular user with the "Login" button.
Username: sourceforge
Password: sourceforge
Enjoy!
